## Verification Plan

### Steps
1. **Seed the database** â€” run `npm run seed` in the backend to create admin user and sample products
2. **Test admin login** â€” login with `admin@yobazar.com` / `Admin@123`, verify redirect to `/admin`
3. **Test product creation** â€” go to `/admin/products/add`, fill form with images, verify product appears
4. **Test user purchase flow** â€” register a user, browse shop, add to cart, checkout, verify order confirmation page
5. **Test emails** â€” check both user email and admin email (`sethysaiyangyadatta@gmail.com`) receive order notification
6. **Test admin order management** â€” login as admin, go to `/admin/orders`, update an order status
